DESCRIPTION:Treat yourself (and someone you love) to two of our favorite t
 hings that are both delicious and good for you. Learn about the health ben
 efits of our extra-virgin organic olive oil\, then pair it with high-quali
 ty organic chocolate to make Chocolate Olive Oil Mousse and a glossy Glaze
 d Chocolate Orange Olive Oil Cake.\n\nWhat to Expect:\n\n\\*A demonstratio
 n-style class in our charming Apple Cottage kitchen\n\n\\*Tastings of the 
 finished products\n\n\\*A ride to and from the Apple Cottage in our apple-
 themed trolley\n\n\\*10% off all Farm Shop purchases made on the day of th
 e workshop\n\nStephanie Rosenbaum Klassen\, our Farm Shop lead\, brings ye
 ars of experience as a cookbook author\, teacher\, and food writer. Her ac
 claimed books include A Little Taste of San Francisco\, World of Doughnuts
 \, and Honey from Flower to Table. Her work has appeared in The New York T
 imes\, San Francisco Chronicle\, Edible publications\, and more.
