BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:"You're My Neighbor" Art Exhibit - Opening Reception
DTSTART;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T130000
DTEND;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T150000
UID:260227lC5QxiVQDEOZLul3KBV1bw
DESCRIPTION:Come out to Point Reyes and celebrate neighbors!   \n\nJoin 
 us for the opening reception of Cedars “You’re My Neighbor!” From mo
 oing cows and soaring birds to friendly faces down the road\, Cedars artis
 ts take a joyful look at their Marin County neighborhood. This exhibition 
 explores all the things that make their corner of the world special—open
  fields\, wild creatures\, familiar people\, and the everyday moments in b
 etween. Through colorful\, thoughtful\, and imaginative works\, “You’r
 e My Neighbor” celebrates the beauty of living side by side and sharing 
 a place we call home.\n\nOpening Reception: Saturday\, March 7\, 1pm to 3p
 m\n\nExhibition dates: March 3 through April 1
