DESCRIPTION:Take a last look at Julia with a free event at The MAC featu
 ring **Bella Union Winery**\, on the final weekend of our inaugural e
 xhibition: “**Julia Child: A Recipe for Life”** \n\nDate: Saturday\,
  March 7\, 2026 Time: 1-4 p.m. Location: The Napa Valley Museum of Art
  & Culture (The MAC)  \n\nJoin us for a warm and welcoming afternoon as
  we partner with **Bella Union Winery** for a special farewell tribute
  event. Enjoy a selection of exceptional wines by Bella Union Winery in c
 elebration of Julia Child and her joyful approach to life\, and browse 
 the museum store at no charge.  Enjoy special discounts on select Ju
 lia Child inspired merchandise. **Purchase tickets** to experience 
 “**Julia Child: A Recipe for Life\,”** an immersive exhibition celebr
 ating the iconic chef and broadcasting pioneer. The wine tasting is open 
 to all visitors 21+\n\nIt’s hard to believe that our first exhibition a
 t The MAC is coming to its end\, but our national tour of "Julia Child
 : A Recipe for Life" continues. The exhibition officially closes March
  8\, 2026\, at 5 PM. Come raise a glass with us and celebrate\, Julia 
 Child\, whose legacy continues to inspire.
