BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:From Spirit with Love a Council Gathering of the Ancestors
DTSTART;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T150000
DTEND;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T170000
UID:260222bDGwQZtUv0SjsIpYUGaxnw
DESCRIPTION:With more than 50 years of experience and five advanced degree
 s\, Dr. Maria is known worldwide as a medical intuitive\, channel\, empath
 \, teacher\, and Lakota/Diné Traditional Elder.\n\nDuring this time of g
 reat upheaval in our world\, and specifically in our country\, the environ
 ments we live in and create for ourselves can have dramatic impacts on our
  cellular healing and processing. Dr. Maria Michael will talk about how cl
 imate change\, social justice and our environments impact our physical\, m
 ental\, emotional and spiritual bodies. She will talk about the importance
  of self care\, focusing on the most impacted organs\, how to recognize wh
 at is needed\, and ways in which to support yourself\, physically\, emotio
 nally\, spiritually\, and mentally. She will focus on herbal medicine and 
 other somatic and ancient methods to support the immune system. There will
  be time for an open dialogue with the audience and to answer questions. W
 hat makes this evening especially powerful is that it takes place within t
 he amplified bioenergetic field of the EESystem. As Dr. Maria speaks about
  cellular resonance\, coherence\, and restoring balance\, guests will simu
 ltaneously be immersed in a scalar-energy environment designed to support 
 optimal cellular communication and energetic harmony. The experience becom
 es more than a lecture — it becomes embodied learning.\n\nThis event off
 ers a welcoming introduction to Dr. Maria’s work. For those who feel ca
 lled to go deeper\, Dr Maria will hold on March 15th a group healing circl
 e ceremony/workshop. It is a guided interactive process\, in which each pa
 rticipant will experience a variety of techniques using light\, sound\, to
 uch\, energy and ancient wisdom healing techniques. Whether you are new to
  her work or already familiar with energy-based healing\, this evening is 
 an invitation to explore what becomes possible when wisdom\, frequency\, a
 nd intention align. We look forward to welcoming you into the field.\n\nAb
 out Dr Maria Michael\n\nDr. Maria D. Michael is a world renowned and respe
 cted medical intuitive\, channel\, empath\, healer\, psychic and teacher f
 or over 40 years. She has been awarded 5 advanced degrees \\(all Summa Cum
  Laude\\)\, including a Ph.D. in Counseling Psychology. She has doctorate-
 level training in Neuropsychology and Special Education and extensive post
 -doctoral studies in Psychoanalysis and Jungian Psychology. Additionally\,
  Dr. Michael is trained and experienced in EMDR\, Hypnotherapy\, LENS Neur
 ofeedback\, Neurolinguistic Programming\, Eriksonian Hypnosis Training. Sh
 e is a Lakota/Diné \\(Navajo\\) Traditional elder\, has participated in a
 nd led traditional Native ceremonies and doctored alongside Lakota Medicin
 e people. She has been sought out worldwide for her powerful Medicine Ener
 gies and Healing abilities.\n\nBELIEFS\n\nDr. Maria Michael believes that 
 we all come from the same Creation\, and that everyone has the potential a
 nd capacity to communicate with Creation. While the Lakota call Creation 
 “The Great Mystery\,” other traditions may refer to Creation\, with na
 mes such as\, “God\,” “the Universe\,” “Allah\,” “Yahweh\,
 ” “Divine Love\,” “Universal Love” or “Cosmic Consciousness.
 ”\n\nWe not only choose our human families\, but also we choose\, initia
 lly at least\, our own unique form or tradition of understanding and commu
 nication with the Great Mystery. No form or tradition is better than anoth
 er. Humans are merely attempting to understand “That” which is beyond 
 comprehension.\n\nAll messages from the Great Mystery are compassionate an
 d loving\, even though at times these messages may appear difficult. Creat
 ion’s message appears to us in whatever way we choose to comprehend it. 
 Sometimes\, we are only capable of comprehending deeply sensitive messages
  that resound in our hearts\, and sometimes only strong and “seemingly
 ” shocking messages penetrate our defenses. This loving Spirit guides us
  to remove those obstacles that stand in our way of becoming all that Crea
 tion and We intended us to be.
LOCATION:Energy Wave Center
URL:https://energywavecenter.com/maria-michael/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
