DESCRIPTION:Please join us for a delightful afternoon of Bunco on Saturday
 \, March 7! This game is for both newbies and bunco pros- all are welcome!
  Your $40 ticket includes the game\, prizes\, drinks\, and finger foods. A
 nd let's not forget the fun!\n\nNo worries if you've never played bunco be
 fore- it's easy peasy! Bunco is a group dice game where you get to mix and
  mingle with all of the players. No skill necessary\, just bring your smil
 e and be ready to roll the dice.\n\nProceeds from this fundraiser support 
