BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Wreckless Strangers at Rancho Nicasio
DTSTART;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T193000
DTEND;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T230000
UID:260219YjLKnqOqoUGLNNGhZZLL6w
DESCRIPTION:Coming off the heels of a lively\, full-house record release s
 how at Sweetwater\, **Wreckless Strangers** continue their album release c
 elebration with a special dinner show at the legendary West Marin roadhous
 e **Rancho Nicasio** on **Saturday\, March 7\,** joined by special guests
 \, including a horn section alongside the six-piece band. The Bay Area sex
 tet is thrilled to bring their signature sound back to the iconic venue. M
 usic begins at **7:30 pm**\, with dinner reservations available from **6 p
 m to 8 pm**.\n\nWreckless Strangers return to their roots with their forth
 coming studio album\, ***Dirty Souls***. The six-song collection marks the
  band’s most raw and visceral effort to date — a modern take on the ar
 ena rock of the 1970s and ’80s that inspired their earliest musical infl
 uences.\n\nThe songwriting is among their most intimate and personal\, exp
 loring themes of relationships\, loss\, empowerment\, and perseverance. Co
 -lead singers **Amber Morris** and **David Noble** function as a single o
 rganism\, bringing the songs to life with bluesy grit\, soul\, and humanit
 y bolstered by rock-solid\, road-hewn grooves. \n\n***Dirty Souls*** is 
 the band’s third studio outing under the tutelage of Grammy-winning prod
 ucer **Dave Way**\, who fosters a level of depth and organic cohesion that
  firmly establishes Wreckless Strangers in San Francisco’s storied rock 
 ‘n’ roll legacy.  The first single\, "Dirty Soul\," came out on Janua
 ry 23 and is available on all streaming platforms. The full album comes ou
 t in late March\, but concert attendees will have the exclusive opportunit
 y to purchase advance copies of the CD. Review copies are available now\, 
 upon request.\n\nVisit **WrecklessStrangers.com** and follow the band on 
 social media for updates.
LOCATION:Rancho Nicasio
URL:https://www.wrecklessstrangers.com/home#Shows
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Dirty Cello
