DESCRIPTION:Come explore the Vallejo waterfront! 🌊\n\nJoin the Solano B
 ayshore Resiliency Project on an engaging\, free sea level rise walking to
 ur starting at the Vallejo Ferry Terminal at 11am! You can expect: snacks\
 , coffee\, breakfast\, and expert insights from Jeremy Lowe\, Senior Envir
 onmental Scientist at the San Francisco Estuary Institute. \n\nWe want to
  hear about any concerns you may have about sea level rise impacts in Vall
 ejo\, your relationship to the shoreline\, and solutions you hope to see i
 n the future. Together\, we can ensure Vallejo shoreline communities remai
 n resilient and thriving for years to come! \n\nPlus: drop by our table a
 t the Vallejo Ferry Terminal anytime from 9:30-1:00 P.M. to join our commu
 nity mapping activity and be entered to win a $50 gift card!
LOCATION:Vallejo Ferry Terminal
