UID:260123Q2OMsL4x2E6C6JBFJoAicA
DESCRIPTION:\\[Translated to English below\\] ¿Qué tipo de pájaro es es
 e? Agarra tus binoculares y tu familia y acompáñanos en una aventura avi
 aria el sábado\, 7 de marzo\, 2026. Empezaremos hablando acerca de las di
 ferentes herramientas que podemos utilizar para identificar pájaros\, com
 o guías de campo\, binoculares\, y aplicaciones móviles. Durante la cami
 nata\, te enseñaremos pistas para ayudarte a identificar específicas esp
 ecies por vista\, sonido\, vuelo\, y/o comportamiento.\n\nEvento gratuito\
 ; requiere registración. Hay transportación disponible gratuita dentro d
 e un radio de 20 millas al parque para familias que la necesiten. Para det
 alles y registración\, visita sec.regfox.com/aves2026\n\nAlternativamente
 \, llama a Mario (707-387-4087)\, Alma (707-247-5767\, entre martes y sáb
 ado) o escríbenos a senderos@sonomaecologycenter.org. ¿No puedes acompa
 ñarnos ese día? ¡Guarda la fecha el 7 marzo para más aventuras!\n\nSen
 deros Naturales es parcialmente respaldado por una beca de Parks Californi
 a.\n\n\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\n\nWhat bird is that? Grab your binoc
 ulars and family and join us on an avian adventure on Saturday\, March 7\,
  2026. This event is planned around a primarily Latino audience and will b
 e conducted in Spanish. Families from underrepresented groups are welcome 
 to join. Free transportation available within a 20 mile radius of the park
  for families in need. For questions\, please email senderos@sonomaecology
 center.org\n\nSenderos Naturales is supported by a grant from Parks Califo
 rnia.
LOCATION:Sugarloaf Ridge State Park
URL:https://sec.regfox.com/aves2026
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:SHAWN LANGWELL PRESENTS - FREE MASTERCLASS: BEYOND GOALSETTING
DTSTART;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T093000
DTEND;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T110000
UID:2601195P9wXt02WU6Vj-OjDDqd4g
DESCRIPTION:FREE BEYOND GOAL SETTING MASTERCLASS with Shawn Langwell\n\nWh
 y Trying Harder Isn’t Working — and What Actually Does\n\nA 90-Minute 
 interactive workshop for ambitious people who are tired of feeling stresse
 d out and stuck.\n\nFrom the author of Ten Seconds of Boldness and Beyo
 nd Recovery\n\nYou’ve done what you were taught to do:\n\nSet goals. Mad
 e plans. Pushed harder. Try to stay disciplined.\n\nAnd yet… something s
 till isn’t moving.\n\nThis workshop is for people who are doing “the r
 ight things” — in life\, work\, business\, leadership\, or creative en
 deavors — but feel stuck\, stalled\, or quietly frustrated underneath it
  all.\n\nNot because you’re lazy. Not because you’re broken. But becau
 se there are things no one ever taught you in school.\n\nWHAT THEY DON’T
  TEACH YOU\n\nThey don’t teach you how to:\n\n• Move forward when conf
 idence hasn’t shown up yet\n\n• Stop overthinking without giving up re
 sponsibility\n\n• Take action when clarity is incomplete• Make progres
 s without burning yourself out\n\n• Lead yourself \\(and others\\) throu
 gh uncertainty with integrity\n\nThis session is grounded in decades of re
 al-world experience — not theory\, hype\, or hustle culture.\n\nEverythi
 ng you’ll hear has been lived\, tested\, failed at\, adjusted\, and prac
 ticed in real careers\, real leadership roles\, and real life.\n\nWHAT THI
 S WORKSHOP IS ABOUT\n\nThis is not a goal-setting seminar.\n\nIt’s a pra
 ctical\, human conversation about:\n\n• Why people stay stuck in plannin
 g and preparation\n\n• How clarity actually shows up \\(it doesn’t com
 e first\\)\n\n• Why willingness matters more than readiness\n\n• How s
 mall\, bold and honest steps create real momentum\n\nYou’ll be invited t
 o slow down\, get honest\, and reconnect with what actually matters right 
 now — without pressure or performance.\n\nYOU WILL LEARN HOW TO:\n\n• 
 Recognize where overthinking is keeping you stuck\n\n• Get clear about w
 hat you really want \\(not what you think you should want\\)\n\n• Stop w
 aiting to feel ready before you begin\n\n• Replace pressure with willing
 ness\n\n• Take meaningful action even when confidence isn’t there yet\
 n\nYOU WILL WALK AWAY WITH:\n\n• Greater clarity about what’s actually
  holding you back\n\n• Relief from self-imposed pressure• A renewed se
 nse of direction\n\n• One honest\, doable next step forward\n\n• A pra
 ctical way to move without burning out\n\nNo hype. No fixing. No pretendin
 g.\n\nJust grounded movement.\n\nABOUT THE FACILITATOR\n\nShawn Langwell i
 s an Inspirational Author\, Teacher\, and Sales & Executive Gap Mindset Co
 ach/Consultant with more than three decades of sales and leadership experi
 ence.\n\nHe is the author of Beyond Recovery\, Ten Seconds of Boldness \\(
 and its companion workbook\\)\, Morning Motivation\, and Chill.\n\nHis wor
 k is grounded\, practical\, and focused on real change — without hype\, 
 dogma\, or pressure.\n\nLearn more at www.shawnlangwell.com\n\nREADY TO TA
 KE THE NEXT BOLD STEP FORWARD?\n\nFor those who are ready\, this workshop 
 opens the door to deeper live workshops and 1:1 coaching designed to help 
 you take the next bold steps forward — and begin manifesting the goals a
 nd changes you’ve been thinking about for far too long.\n\nNo pressure. 
 Just alignment.\n\nThat’s where alignment begins — and overwhelm ends.
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/shawn-langwell-presents-free-masterclass-
 beyond-goalsetting-tickets-1979676084460
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
