DTEND;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T160000
UID:260304wMDiIiyI6kyJ4gg-G135yQ
DESCRIPTION:In celebration of its 50th Anniversary\, Wine Road's signature
  Barrel Weekend returns for a full weekend experience. A cherished traditi
 on of the Wine Road\, Barrel Weekend invites guests to sample wines straig
 ht from the barrel\, just as the winemaker does. Step into the cellar\, me
 et the vintners\, and gain insight into their craft and philosophy. While 
 the focus is on wine rather than food pairings\, guests are encouraged to 
 pack a picnic and enjoy lunch on the beautiful winery grounds. In addition
  to barrel tastings\, many wineries will pour current releases ready to en
 joy\, and select locations may offer rare library wines offering a unique 
 chance to experience the past\, present\, and future of winemaking in one 
 immersive weekend. Single-day tickets are not available\; groups of eight 
 or more are not permitted.
LOCATION:Various Sonoma County Locations
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/wineroad-barrel-tasting-weekend/
