UID:260304ui44sKiKaECaE1lkU7n_1Q
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the vibrant arrival of the season with an exclusive 
 evening at our Upper Ranch. We invite you to join us for a casual\, sensor
 y-rich gathering designed to delight the palate and restore the spirit. \n
 \nThe afternoon begins in our Upper Ranch gardens\, where dozens of tulips
  are currently putting on a spectacular show. Stroll through rows of brill
 iant color\, taking in the peak bloom while enjoying a curated selection o
 f small bites and McEvoy Ranch wines. It is the perfect moment to reconnec
 t with friends and soak in the golden hour light over the hills. \n\nAs du
 sk settles\, we will transition to the serenity of our Pavilion for a rest
 orative Sound Bath. Let the resonant sounds wash over you\, grounding your
  energy and providing a peaceful conclusion to a day of beauty. \n\nExperi
 ence the ranch in full bloom—a feast for the eyes\, a treat for the pala
 te\, and a balm for the soul. \n\nTicket: $48 \\+ Processing Fee \n\nMembe
 r Ticket: 15% off \n\nThe Estate: 4 guests\n\nThe ODE Haven\, Orchard\, & 
 Vineyard: 2 guests
