UID:260303aK6BuIIX3UiaJ1_gXY8J3w
DESCRIPTION:Be transported back in time by the sounds of the Paris café m
 usic scene of the 1900s. Led by Parisian singer Mimi Pirard\, SonoMusette 
 authentically recreates the evocative sounds of the Paris café music scen
 e of the 1900s. The songs of Edith Piaf\, Jacques Brel\, Charles Aznavour\
 , Barbara\, and other iconic performers of 20th Century Paris. Be transpor
 ted back in time by the sounds of musette accordion\, piano\, guitar\, bas
 s\, drum set\, and stunning vocals. All songs performed in the original Fr
 ench language. This music has retained its power to charm and transport li
 steners\, and SonoMusette taps that nostalgia with artistry in both vocals
  and instrumentation. Mimi Pirard - vocals Robert Lunceford - accordion Ja
 n Martinelli - piano & bass Isaac Vandeveer - guitar & bass Kendrick Freem
 an - drum set. Video Link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Alp6ppMjD1g BUY
