 erspective\, and the uncomfortable truths of performance itself. Lexus Fle
 tcher – Actor 6/Black Woman Thomas Peterson – Actor 1/White Man Isiah 
 Carter – Actor 2/Black Man Nate Musser – Actor 3/Another White Man Sam
  Minnifield – Actor 4/Another Black Man Maddi Scarbrough – Actor 5/Sar
