BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Safari West Presents! Oiled Wildlife Care Network
DTSTART;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T200000
DTEND;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T203000
UID:251216k7ftl70q-kST-h5QwL0gDA
DESCRIPTION:Conservation Dinner Series: Lorraine Barbosa from  Oiled Wildl
 ife Care Network joins us in the elephant room after dinner to give a talk
  about the veterinary care of oiled sea life. The conservation dinner seri
 es is complimentary to all dinner guests. If you want to attend this prese
 ntation\, please call our reservations team at \\(707\\) 566-3667 or \\(80
 0\\) 616-2695 and they can book it for you. Dinner starts at 7:00 PM.    A
 bout the Speaker: Lorraine obtained her veterinary degree and Masters of P
 reventive Veterinary Medicine from UC Davis in 2010 and has since spent he
 r time working as both a small animal and wildlife veterinarian. Her main 
 focus has been on marine mammals\, specifically pinnipeds \\(seals and sea
  lions\\)\, but during her years as a veterinarian\, she has worked with a
  variety of wildlife\, everything birds to bears. In addition to clinical 
 work\, Lorraine has also enjoyed collaborating on several marine mammal fi
 eld research projects in Central and South America. In 2017 she became cer
 tified as a Diplomate of the American College of Preventive Veterinary Med
 icine\, and in 2018 she began working as a veterinarian for the Oiled Wild
 life Care Network at UC Davis\, where she currently serves as the Senior M
 anager of Care Operations.
LOCATION:Safari West
URL:https://safariwest.com/calendar/safari-west-presents-oiled-wildlife-ca
 re-network/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
