BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Bachata Beginners Saturday
DTSTART;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T090000
DTEND;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T100000
UID:2512134SgVLfFo2EWmz0loJp-UEQ
DESCRIPTION:This class is perfect for bachata beginners that want to learn
  basic steps and skills\, or those who want to refresh their foundational 
 skills. We understand that learning something new can feel a little intimi
 dating. That’s why our supportive and relaxed environment is specificall
 y designed to make learning bachata basics an absolute blast!\n\nOur frien
 dly instructors will guide you through:\n\nBasic directional steps: You
 ’ll learn the fundamental movements that form the building blocks of all
  bachata dancing.\n\nProper frame for partner work: Discover how to conne
 ct comfortably and effectively with a partner\, setting you up for smooth 
 and enjoyable dances.\n\nSimple turn patterns: We’ll introduce you to e
 asy-to-follow turn patterns that will have you dancing with a partner in n
 o time.\n\nWe’ve carefully organized our curriculum to ensure that each 
 movement is easy to grasp and remember\, building your confidence with eve
 ry step. Our goal is to make learning fun. Join us to learn Bachata in Mar
 in.\n\nImportant Details\n\nNo dance experience required: Whether you’v
 e never danced before or it’s been a while\, you’re welcome here!\n\nN
 o partner necessary: Come solo or bring a friend—either way\, you’ll 
 have plenty of opportunities to dance.\n\nPlease wear non-marking shoe so
 les: This helps us keep our dance floor in great condition.\n\nCome join 
 us and discover the joy of bachata! We can’t wait to see you on the danc
 e floor.\n\nDate & Time:\n\nThursdays @ 6:30PM – 7:30PM Fridays @ 5:30PM
  – 6:30PM Saturdays @ 9:00 AM – 10:00 AM\n\nInstructor: Lucie Ebnerova
 \n\nAddress: 4140 Redwood Highway \\#8 San Rafael\, CA\n\nNote: Arrive 10 
 minutes before. No floor marking shoe soles allowed.
LOCATION:4140 Redwood Highway #8 San Rafael
URL:https://salsadancemarin.com/bachata-beginners/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Salsa Beginner Marin – Saturday
DTSTART;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T100000
DTEND;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260307T110000
UID:251212yCbKJ4Vbqk24w5IdmHp5Vw
DESCRIPTION:**Ready to learn intermediate steps and technique?** Join on 
 on Saturday – Salsa Beginner Marin\n\nAre you a beginner who’s always 
 wanted to learn salsa? Salsa classes are designed to help you build a stro
 ng foundation. In this class\, you’ll learn the fundamental footwork\, p
 ractice the basic turns\, and understand the essential body movement that 
 will make you feel confident on the dance floor. This class is perfect for
  anyone ready to learn the techniques and foundational steps needed to sta
 rt their salsa journey.\n\nSalsa is fun\, and we make learning it stress-f
 ree! Our relaxed\, beginner-friendly class is the ideal starting point. Yo
 u don’t need a partner\, nor any dance experience!\n\nIn this class you 
 will learn:\n\nBasic directional steps that form the foundation of salsa.\
 n\nProper frame for comfortable and effective partner-work.\n\nSimple\, ea
 sy-to-remember turn patterns.\n\nGet ready to learn the fundamentals and h
 ave a great time!\n\n**Details:**\n\n**No partner necessary**—rotations 
 ensure everyone dances\n\nPlease wear **non-marking shoes** to protect t
 he floor\n\nArrive 10 minutes early\; warm up and settle in\n\n**When:** 
 Saturday\, 10:00 am – 11:00 am\n\n**Where:** 4140 Redwood Highway #8\, 
 San Rafael\, CA
LOCATION:4140 Redwood Highway #8\, San Rafael\, CA
URL:https://salsadancemarin.com/salsa-beginners-saturday/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
