SUMMARY:March Month of Flowers Challenge
DTSTART;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T000000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T120000
UID:260306X1VnUuI2pk2tUt4Vlj6CYw
DESCRIPTION:Starting March 1st begins the "March Month of Flowers Challeng
 e" \\(online\\). \n\nYou'll receive a list of prompts for every day in Mar
 ch. \n\nCreate an art piece related to the prompt.\n\nShare in our privat
 e Facebook group.\n\nBe inspired and give inspiration to others.\n\nOnly $
 5\, so everyone can join and share in this creative adventure!\n\nMarch Mo
 nth of Flowers Challenge is here to give you a creative outlet\, some st
 ructure\, and respite from your brain. \n\nWhen you pick up a brush\, pen
 \, or pencil \\(thread\, clay\, fabric…\\)\, your brain gets a rest and 
 becomes more alive and flexible. The world around you becomes more alive\
 ; you pick up on shades\, details\, and patterns all around you. Your in
 tuition gets stronger. And fear lessens\, anxiety fades\, and curiosity gr
 ows. You stop worrying about making mistakes\, and instead\, you find the
  freedom to simply create
URL:https://www.taradickinson.com/project-page/workshops
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Bottle Baby Breakfast Club
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T100000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T160000
UID:260305fPCKGNBC-UaDwMCMmBpqBA
DESCRIPTION:**Tiny Hooves\, Big Hearts: Our Ongoing Rescue Mission**\n\n**
 At Goatlandia\, our mission is simple: to give love\, safety\, and a secon
 d chance to animals who need it most.**\n\n**We were recently called to re
 scue three baby goats. These tiny babies are now safe at Goatlandia\, and 
 they need bottle feeding several times a day to stay healthy and thrive.**
 \n\n**That’s Where You Come In: The Bottle Baby Breakfast Club**\n\n**St
 arting March 6th\, join us for a heartwarming hour on the farm\, bottle-fe
 eding and cuddling our newest rescues while supporting their care.**\n\n**
 Your $250 donation (covers milk and supplies for weeks of feedings) includ
 es admission for up to four guests for a private\, unforgettable visit to 
 Goatlandia.**\n\n**Come share the love\, feel the magic\, and help us give
  these little ones the future they deserve.**
LOCATION:Goatlandia
URL:https://www.goatlandia.org/bottle-babies-breakfast-club
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Just Between Friends North Bay Children's Consignment Event
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T100000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T160000
UID:260305V3ghyqdGnk-xZbWTQmJnLA
DESCRIPTION:Just Between Friends North Bay Spring Kids Consignment Sale | 
 March 6–8\, Santa Rosa\n\nLooking for affordable children’s clothing\,
  toys\, and baby gear in the North Bay? The Just Between Friends \\(JBF\\)
  North Bay Spring Sale returns March 6–8 with one of the largest childre
 n’s consignment shopping events in the region. This spring\, the sale wi
 ll be held at a new location inside the Santa Rosa Plaza\, in the former S
 ears space.\n\nThe JBF North Bay Spring Sale is a massive pop-up resale ev
 ent where local families sell thousands of gently used and new children’
 s items at deeply discounted prices. Shoppers can find everything they nee
 d for babies\, kids\, and teens—often saving 50–90% off retail.\n\nSho
 p Thousands of Kids’ Items in One Place This family-friendly shopping ev
 ent features a wide selection of:\n\nChildren’s clothing \\(baby through
  teen sizes\\)\n\nShoes\, jackets\, and accessories\n\nToys\, books\, game
 s\, and puzzles\n\nBaby gear including strollers\, swings\, and high chair
 s\n\nNursery items\, kids’ décor\, sports gear\, and more\n\nIt’s an 
 easy one-stop shop for families preparing for a new baby\, refreshing ward
 robes for spring and summer\, or stocking up on toys and essentials.\n\nWh
 y North Bay Families Love This Sale Instead of visiting multiple stores or
  searching online listings\, shoppers can browse thousands of items in one
  organized indoor space. Families throughout Santa Rosa and the North Bay 
 return each season for the convenience\, variety\, and unbeatable savings.
 \n\nNew Venue: Santa Rosa Plaza \\(Former Sears Space\\) The Spring Sale w
 ill take place at Santa Rosa Plaza\, inside the former Sears location\, of
 fering a spacious and comfortable indoor shopping experience in a central 
 Santa Rosa location.\n\nFree Tickets and Free Parking Admission is free wi
 th online tickets\, and free parking is available\, making this an accessi
 ble and budget-friendly event for families.\n\nEvent Dates\n\nThursday\, M
 arch 5: Special ticketed presale day\n\nFriday–Sunday\, March 6–8: Ope
 n shopping days\n\nIf you’re searching for a kids consignment sale in Sa
 nta Rosa\, a family shopping event in the North Bay\, or a smart way to sa
 ve on children’s items this spring\, the Just Between Friends North Bay 
 Spring Sale is a must-visit event.
LOCATION:Santa Rosa Plaza
URL:https://northbay.jbfsale.com/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
