DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T190000
UID:260302omr06D0KSEKJcwIfYVWd6w
DESCRIPTION:A coalition of community members\, parents\, and local busines
 s owners are hosting a fundraiser for VIDAS \\( Vital\, Immigrant\, Defens
 e Advocacy & Services\\)- an organization that provides trauma-informed im
 migration legal advocacy. VIDAS envisions safe passage\, universal represe
 ntation\, and a humane migration system for all. VIDAS has five locations 
 throughout Sonoma County. VIDAS offers life-changing legal representation\
 , training\, mental health services\, and community organizing that empowe
 rs immigrant families. This is an evening featuring incredible food\, drin
 ks\, sweets\, performance art\, live music\, poetry\, an art salon\, and a
  silent auction.
LOCATION:Altamont General Store
URL:https://www.altamontgeneralstore.com/event-details-registration/a-call
 -for-care-a-fundraiser-for-vidas-vital-immigrant-defense-advocacy-services
 /form
