DESCRIPTION:Join parent\, pro cyclist and all-around bike champion Lariss
 a Connors on this fun family ride from Santa Rosa to Sebastopol on the Joe
  Rodota Trail. Meet at the trailhead on Sebastopol Road just off Wright Ro
 ad. Ride to the Barlow \\(bring some cash for treats\\)\, and ride back fo
 r a total of 7 miles!\n\nOpen to all kids and families! Bikes must be in w
 orking order\, and ALL RIDERS MUST HAVE HELMETS TO PARTICIPATE. Kids must 
 be able to ride a two-wheeled bike or may participate in bike seats\, trai
 lers or trail-a-bikes.\n\nKids under 12 must be accompanied by an adult. K
 ids 12 and older must have a parent sign the participation waiver upon reg
 istration.\n\nDid we mention helmets are required?
