BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:"You're My Neighbor" Art Exhibit
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T100000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T170000
UID:260227s-3CP9VMw0eFHsA58_KYfw
DESCRIPTION:Come out to Point Reyes and celebrate neighbors!   \n\nFrom 
 mooing cows and soaring birds to friendly faces down the road\, Cedars art
 ists take a joyful look at their Marin County neighborhood. This exhibitio
 n explores all the things that make their corner of the world special—op
 en fields\, wild creatures\, familiar people\, and the everyday moments in
  between. Through colorful\, thoughtful\, and imaginative works\, “You
 ’re My Neighbor” celebrates the beauty of living side by side and shar
 ing a place we call home.\n\n​Cedars “You’re My Neighbor!” art exh
 ibition runs from March 3 through April 12\, 2026
LOCATION:Toby's Feed Barn
URL:https://www.cedarslife.org/events
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:An Abstract Vision
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T110000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260308T180000
UID:260227o9zAkr-hzEmRi4qWBKQO7A
DESCRIPTION:**Exhibition runs April 4 - May 30\, 2026**\n\nDeadline for En
 tries: March 9\, 2026\n\nAn Abstract Vision celebrates the work of artists
  creating abstract art.\n\nAbstract art moves beyond representation\, with
  a strong emphasis on shape\, color and form. Abstract art has the power t
 o evoke emotions\, appeal to our senses and transcend the physical world. 
 Abstract expression captures the delicate\, elusive\, powerful and radiant
  energies that fly under the radar of explanation.\n\nWe are excited to ha
 ve you share with us your visions in the abstract and look forward to putt
 ing together a dynamic exhibition of work that reflects the power and impo
 rtance of abstract art.\n\nAccepting the following mediums: painting\, pri
 ntmaking\, photographs\, sculpture\, glass\, wood\, ceramics\, fiber and p
 aper.
LOCATION:Healdsburg Center for the Arts
URL:https://healdsburgcenterforthearts.org/an-abstract-vision/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
