UID:2602162yxNN8mEJ0KcD56ni2Smlw
DESCRIPTION:This will be an intimate evening connecting with loved ones wh
 o have passed over\, bringing messages of love\, hope and who knows what e
 lse they may have to share.\n\nEach guest is invited to ask a loved one a 
 question or communicate a message .These conversation can bring reassuranc
 e\, closure or a new perspective. Be prepared to be touched and inspired.\
 n\nWhat happens in a Mediumship session?\n\nWith your permission\, I conne
 ct with a loved one who has passed and transmit messages between the two o
 f you.\n\nThe conversation might be one to get an update on how that Spiri
 t is doing\, clarify something that occurred\, forgive one another\, or ge
 t suggestions from the loved one about a concern you have. These conversat
 ions bring relief\, healing and a sense of peace.
