DESCRIPTION:Wine Road's Annual Barrel Tasting California's Longest-Running
  Wine Event Celebrate our 50th anniversary with a $50 ticket Celebrate one
  of Sonoma County's most beloved wine traditions at Wine Road's Annual Bar
 rel Tasting. Now in its 48th year\, this iconic event brings together 50 w
 ineries across Northern Sonoma County for a one-of-a-kind tasting experien
 ce focused on the Past\, Present\, and Future of wine. Meet the winemakers
 \, step into the cellar\, and taste wines straight from the barrel\, along
 side limited-release and library selections. This immersive weekend offers
  a rare behind-the-scenes look at Sonoma County winemaking and the stories
  behind the wines. Barrel Tasting happens just once a year. Come ready to 
 explore\, learn\, sip\, and savor. It's an experience no wine lover should
  miss.
