 ssions – 8 weeks: $265 Registration Fee $30 Materials Fee $295 Total Reg
 istration Fee\n\nWork independently on personal projects with the direct s
 upport of an instructor by your side in this Independent Projects Class wi
 th Amy Hamley.\n\nWhat you’ll do\n\nThis session has been split into 2\
 , 4 week sessions – you can enroll in each session independently or enro
 ll in both as a package deal!This course is for students interested in exp
