 ct to change. For up to date information visit: sonomalibrary.org/bookclub
 s January 13 - Transcendent Kingdom by Yaa Gyasi February 10 - The Fox Wif
 e by Yangsze Choo March 10 - A Fever in the Heartland by Timothy Egan Apri
 l 14 - The Kamogawa Food Detectives by Hisashi Kashiwai May 12 - The Husba
