DESCRIPTION:**WHAT:** Markham Vineyards Private Tasting: The Cabernet Conn
 oisseur’s Experience\n\n**DATE:**            Begins October 1\
 , 2025\, Offered Daily\n\n**TIME:** 11am-1pm and 2-4pm\n\n**WHERE:**   
