UID:260306vZ-YsQWy_0epd50ptx6bmw
DESCRIPTION:Greg Lamboy is a Northern California singer-songwriter whose p
 erformances combine lyrical honesty\, melodic craft\, and soulful acoustic
  guitar. Known for his confident yet comforting stage presence\, Greg weav
 es together original songs and reimagined favorites that invite listeners 
 to slow down and connect. His music blends strength and sensitivity\, reve
 aling deep emotion without pretense and reminding audiences why live music
  matters. Greg has released five albums and continues to captivate audienc
 es across the region\, both as a solo artist and as frontman for the Ameri
 cana band Pacific Standard.
