DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260312T210000
UID:260225ASrvsx3no0esr49rK45Nqw
DESCRIPTION:Greg Lamboy has called Finnegan's Marin home for over a decade
 . Every second Thursday of the month\, this Tiburon-based troubadour settl
 es into the warmly lit corner of Novato's beloved neighborhood pub and doe
 s what he does best: connects. An accomplished guitarist and award-winning
  songwriter\, Lamboy has earned his stripes across the Bay Area scene both
  as a solo artist and as frontman of Pacific Standard\, his soulful Americ
 ana band. His five acclaimed albums draw praise for melodies that are pitc
 h-perfect and lyrics that feel like they were written specifically for you
 . At Finnegan's\, a lively Irish pub and American bar and grill along a tr
 ee-lined street in downtown Novato\, Lamboy's intimate style is perfectly 
 at home. No pretense. No distance. Just a strong clear voice\, commanding 
 guitar\, and songs that\, as one critic put it\, lift you above the everyd
 ay. Come early\, grab a pint\, and let the music find you. https://greglam
 boy.com/\n\n*Every second Thursday of the month | Finnegan's Marin\, 877 G
 rant Ave\, Novato | Free*
LOCATION:Finnegan's Marin
URL:https://www.finnegansmarin.com/events-calendar/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
