UID:260307di8AvwY9vEu1CvphQsD-hQ
DESCRIPTION:Join chef and food preservationist Merrilee Olson\, founder of
  Preserve Farm Kitchens\, at Gold Ridge Organic Farms for a hands-on works
 hop celebrating the vibrant flavors of citrus.\n\nWith years of experience
  transforming farm-fresh ingredients into culinary treasures\, Merrilee wi
 ll share her expert techniques and secrets for making perfectly preserved 
 Meyer Lemons and beautifully candied citrus peel. In this immersive 2.5-ho
 ur class held in our rustic Apple Cottage\, you'll work with organic citru
 s\, learning traditional preservation methods in a relaxed\, hands-on sett
 ing.\n\nYou'll leave with your own jar of handcrafted preserved lemons\, a
  keepsake apple blossom pink apron\, and a bag of organic citrus from our 
 farm so you can practice your new skills at home.\n\nYour experience inclu
 des a scenic ride through the farm aboard our apple-themed trolley or appl
 e blossom-pink VW van\, plus morning tea.
