SUMMARY:Empanadas: Sweet and Savory
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260313T170000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260313T200000
UID:260302mHG-hx1J_kuRFff7yRHtqg
DESCRIPTION:Schedule\n\nFriday\, March 13\, 2026 5:00 PM – 8:00 PM\n\nEx
 perience Level\n\nAll Levels\n\nBilingual\, Culinary Arts\n\nAge\\(s\\)\n\
 n18 and older\n\n$100 – Registration Cost Master the art of empanada mak
 ing with both sweet and savory fillings. Learn dough techniques\, folding 
 methods\, and create delicious handheld pastries.\n\nWhat you’ll do\n\nD
 iscover the versatility of empanadas in this hands-on culinary class where
  you’ll master both sweet and savory variations of this beloved pastry. 
 Learn to create tender\, flaky dough from scratch and explore traditional 
 filling techniques that balance flavor and texture. You’ll prepare savor
 y empanadas with options like seasoned beef\, chicken\, cheese and vegetab
 les\, alongside sweet versions featuring fruit\, chocolate\, or dulce de l
 eche. Instruction covers proper dough handling\, folding and crimping tech
 niques for beautiful presentation\, and cooking methods including baking a
 nd frying. You’ll understand how to adjust moisture levels in fillings t
 o prevent soggy pastries and learn tips for making empanadas ahead for eas
 y entertaining. Whether you’re drawn to traditional Latin American recip
 es or creative fusion flavors\, this class gives you the skills to make pr
 ofessional-quality empanadas at home. Perfect for both beginners and exper
 ienced cooks looking to expand their pastry repertoire.
