 t the ranch in grounded\, natural experiences inviting grounded presence\,
  non-linear exploration and gentle transformation. Partake in our unique t
 ried and true holistic somatic practices™ masterfully blended with horse
  time\, creative expression\, and herbal medicine walks. Take some much ne
 eded time to listen to the natural world interwoven with your own wise int
 uition. Whether you’re in a life transition\, seeking clarity\, or simpl
 y longing for more connection\, this time-out offers space to pause\, refl
 ect\, and remember what matters. Remember\, self awareness is your super p
 ower! \n\nMarch 13–15\, 2026 | 10:00 a.m.–5:00 p.m.\n\nCasari Ranch | 
 Santa Rosa\, CA
