BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Wicked Messengers
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T200000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T233000
UID:2603044HoZHv0SkUyvTfDrjKzOoQ
DESCRIPTION:Rooted in the vibrant Bay Area jam band scene\, **Wicked Mess
 engers** brings a fresh interpretation to the timeless songs of Bob Dylan
 \, Neil Young\, Jerry Garcia\, and more. This collective of seasoned music
 ians embodies a deep respect for famous classic songs while infusing their
  performances with a unique and organic flair.\n\nAt the heart of Wicked M
 essengers are guitarist Pat Nevins\, affectionately known as Shakey Zimmer
 man\, brings his dynamic style and heartfelt vocals\, guitar and harmonica
  to the forefront\; Jay Wilcox\, known for his Garcia esqe guitar tone and
  vocals\, contributes his exceptional prowess\, vocals and harmonies\; mul
 ti-instrumentalist Justin Wooster adds depth with his versatile musiciansh
 ip\, from drums to mandolin and vocals. \n\nThe full electric ensemble cr
 eates a rich tapestry of sound\, enhanced by the driving rhythms of drums\
 , keyboard melodies\, bass lines\, and the soulful twang of pedal steel gu
 itar. For a more intimate experience\, Wicked Messengers also offers a cap
 tivating acoustic trio\, showcasing the intricate interplay of guitars and
  mandolin. The trio unit offers up a vast and deep collection of songs. \
 n\nWicked Messengers made its debut on August 9\, 2025 at Sweetwater Music
  Hall with an amazing 8 band member electric show. That show emerged from 
 an Alcazar Theatre\, Carpinteria CA Shakey Zimmerman show with the additio
 n of guitarist Jay Wilcox resulting in an ongoing project with wide sonic 
 reach. \n\nJoin Wicked Messengers on a musical journey that celebrates th
 e spirit of legendary american songwriters while embracing the improvisati
 onal essence of jam band culture with many of the best Bay Area supporting
  musicians. Get ready for a landscape of songs that honors the past and in
 vigorates the present\, as each performance is a unique experience driven 
 by passion and spontaneity.
LOCATION:Sweetwater Music Hall
URL:https://sweetwatermusichall.org/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
