UID:260214H9ctnI_7i0eHrs9INyVFmw
DESCRIPTION:Victory Outreach Santa Rosa is dedicated to serving at-risk yo
 uth through weekly mentorship and leadership programs\, supporting low-inc
 ome families with consistent children and family services\, operating a fr
 ee residential men’s rehabilitation home\, and hosting outreach events t
 hroughout the year for individuals coming out of incarceration and those b
 attling drug addiction. Through these initiatives\, we work to restore hop
 e\, strengthen families\, and transform lives.\n\nTo help expand and stren
 gthen these vital programs\, we are hosting our annual Crab Feed Fundraise
 r\, which brings together community leaders\, families\, and supporters fo
 r an evening with a purpose.\n\nDelicious Dungeness crab\n\nPasta\n\nSalad
