 w\\) Please no socks \\(grippy kind ok\\) or just tights as the floor ca
 n be slippery. Comfortable clothing to move in or dancewear such as leota
 rds\, skirts\, skirted leotards and tights \\(with shoes\\) of any color o
 r style. Please no tutus or pajamas in class. Hair pulled off of face. Dre
 ss in layers as it can go from chilly to warm fast! Being dressed and read
