BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Outback Presents Whitney Cummings: The Big Baby Tour
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T190000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T190000
UID:260305Se1yI_mtyk-ZyZLmoAU2RA
DESCRIPTION:Back to All Shows\n\nOutback Presents \n\nWhitney Cummings: Th
 e Big Baby Tour\n\nSaturday\, March 14\, 2026\n\n7:00 pm\n\nBUY TICKETS \n
 \nWhitney Cummings is a comedian\, actor\, writer\, producer\, director\, 
 and host of the hit podcast Good for You. Best known for creating and star
 ring in the NBC series Whitney and co-creating the syndicated\, Emmy-nomin
 ated CBS comedy 2 Broke Girls\, she has become a leading voice in modern c
 omedy. Cummings has released six stand-up specials\, including Money Shot 
 \\(2010\\)\, I Love You \\(2014\\)\, I’m Your Girlfriend \\(2016\\)\, Ca
 n I Touch It? \\(2019\\)\, Jokes \\(2022\\)\, and her latest\, Mouthy\, wh
 ich debuted on OnlyFans in November 2023. She has also appeared in numerou
 s television series and films\, such as Good Mourning\, Studio 666\, How I
 t Ends\, and FOX’s Accused\, further solidifying her presence on both th
 e big and small screens. \n\nBeyond performing\, Cummings is a successful 
 author and filmmaker. In 2017\, she published her memoir\, I’m Fine… A
 nd Other Lies\, and made her directorial debut with the feature adaptation
  of Louann Brizendine’s bestseller\, The Female Brain. She continues to 
 create\, produce\, and perform across platforms\, bringing her sharp humor
  and fearless perspective to audiences worldwide. She currently lives in L
 os Angeles. \n\nPOST-SHOW VIP MEET & GREET ADD-ON \n\nVIP Ticket to includ
 e: \n\nPost-Show Meet & Greet & Photo with Whitney Cummings.\n\nMeet & Gre
 et ticket DOES NOT include a seat for the show.\n\nA separate show ticket 
 MUST be purchased to attend Meet & Greet.\n\nTHIRD PARTY RESELLERS\n\nDon
 ’t get taken by deceptive online resellers who use bots to buy tickets a
 nd then mark up their prices. The only safe way to protect your purchase a
 nd guarantee the best seats at the lowest cost is to work directly with us
 : through our website\, by phone\, or at our box office in Santa Rosa. Plu
 s\, we’re not bots. Our friendly team members are easily accessible by p
 hone or at the box office to provide customer support.
LOCATION:Luther Burbank Center for the Arts
URL:https://lutherburbankcenter.org/event/whitney-cummings26/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
