UID:260305FR4noDq5_UyigpQfGewAmw
DESCRIPTION:Think you know our City parks well enough to be able to find t
 he elusive leprechauns?! Here’s how it works… --- DETAILS - Beginning 
 March 2\, visit any one of our City parks from the link below and hunt for
  leprechauns! - Leprechauns will be one-foot tall and laminated on card st
 ock. - If you find a leprechaun\, the directions on how and where to colle
 ct your prize will be on the back \\(also listed in the link below\\). The
  first day you can collect a prize is March 2. - Participants will only be
  allowed to win once\, and staff will be tracking each winner’s name. - 
 Staff will re-hide the leprechauns for others to find \\(last date of re-h
 iding is March 17\\). - March 30 will be the last day you can collect a pr
 ize for finding a leprechaun. --- MORE INFORMATION For more information\, 
 including a list of City parks where leprechauns will be hidden\, how to c
 ollect your prize\, and more\, please visit: SRCity.org/LeprechaunTreasure
 Hunt
