UID:2603045yOtjCn6gEOGTb1H5E_AKw
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an inspiring evening at Bartholomew Estate Winery 
 as we celebrate art\, community\, and wine during a special gallery openin
 g featuring local photographer\, Jason Tinacci and local artist\, Porter B
 rooks. Guests are invited to this open house to stroll through the collect
 ion\, meet Porter and Jason in person\, and hear their stories behind the 
 striking images that capture the beauty and spirit of our region. Sip esta
 te wines\, listen to live music\, mingle with fellow art lovers\, and enjo
 y a relaxed\, creative atmosphere —where you might even find the perfect
