  2812 St Helena Hwy North\, St Helena\, CA 94574\n\n           
              707-963-5292\n\n                
         https://markhamvineyards.com/ \n\n**LINK:**        
      https://markhamvineyards.com/visit/winery-experiences/\n\n**DETAI
 LS:**\n\nDiscover the pinnacle of Markham Cabernet Sauvignon. This private
 ly guided tasting features rare library vintages\, limited single-vineyard
  wines\, and an exclusive barrel tasting of The Philanthropist\, our flags
 hip 100% Cabernet Sauvignon\, expertly paired with local cheeses\, charcut
 erie\, and chocolates. A collector’s journey through the past\, present\
 , and future of Napa Valley Cabernet.\n\nEach booking is private and guide
 d by a dedicated Ambassador. Guests will also step inside the Markham wine
 ry to sample a yet-to-be-released vintage of The Philanthropist Cabernet S
 auvignon from a French Oak barrel.\n\n·         **Offered Daily:*
 * 11:00 am – 1:00 pm and 2:00 – 4:00 pm\n\n·         **Experi
 ence length:** 2 hours\n\n·         **Wines:** Selections of libr
 ary\, limited single-vineyard\, and a barrel tasting of yet-to-be-released
  Cabernet Sauvignon\n\n·         **Cost:** $150 per Person\n\n·
          **Exclusive Member Price:** $95 per Member\n\n**ADMISSION
 :** Members $95 | Non-members $150
