BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Beginning Improv Class
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260317T183000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260317T203000
UID:260304AOKAUJMHW0-gxkS4Q36x0g
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to 6-week introduction to the world of improv. It's su
 per fun\, playful and supportive!\n\nWe'll focus on games and exercises de
 signed to get us out of our judging minds and into a playful state of flow
 \, and start exploring scene work while learning the basic elements that m
 ake improv work. You'll learn to think on your feet \\(which actually mean
 s to STOP thinking\\)\, trust your instincts\, and work collaboratively wi
 th others. Expect lots of laughter\, spontaneity\, and unforgettable momen
 ts.\n\nYou don't consider yourself “naturally” quick\, funny or outgoi
 ng? Perfect! You don't need to be to do improv\, all you need to do is sho
 w up--truly! You will surprise yourself\, then watch your confidence grow.
  Improv tools can help us be more comfortable with ourselves\, thus enabli
