UID:260120UHrSVBGuJ06Kb1YAEhc_dg
DESCRIPTION:Join us every week for a casual run from Sports Basement!\n\nW
 e meet Tuesdays at 6pm inside the store and run a loop in the Kawana Sprin
 gs neighborhood.\n\nThe route is about 3 miles and you can run\, walk\, jo
 g\, or any combination!  We leave no runner behind and welcome kids and f
 amilies.\n\nRegular updates can be found on our Strava Page (search for: S
 ports Basement Santa Rosa Run Club)\n\nCome on over\, bring a friend\, and
  stick around for pizza and refreshments after!\n\nFeel free to call the s
 tore with any questions at 707-921-3151
LOCATION:Sports Basement
URL:https://www.strava.com/clubs/santarosarunclub
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
