DESCRIPTION:Downtown Santa Rosa 'Golden Hour' 4-7p| Live music 5-7 p | $6 
 beers & $2 off wine |Tuesday-Saturday!\n\nFor people who like to party...b
 ut want to be home at a reasonable hour...\n\nKen Risling with Avery & Oon
 a - 3rd Tuesdays!\n\nEvenings of covers & originals.\n\nA musician since b
 irth\, Ken has played many instruments in many genres. His first songs wer
 e written while in high school\, but he began writing in earnest at the te
 nder age of 45. He writes for himself and also with an ear to other perfor
 mers. His songs have won numerous awards and airplay. Whenever he can\, he
  performs with his favorite artists.\n\n21+ Happy Hour Pricing 4-6pm All b
 eers - $6 + $2 off wine. Live Music 5-7pm 2 drink minimum\, please\n\nChec
 k out **www.BarrelProofLounge.com** for all sorts of good times ahead!
