DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T120000
UID:260306zcfdcHzdPUqIf9Ld_wSVgg
DESCRIPTION:Starting March 1st begins the "March Month of Flowers Challeng
 e" \\(online\\). \n\nYou'll receive a list of prompts for every day in Mar
 ch. \n\nCreate an art piece related to the prompt.\n\nShare in our privat
 e Facebook group.\n\nBe inspired and give inspiration to others.\n\nOnly $
 5\, so everyone can join and share in this creative adventure!\n\nMarch Mo
 nth of Flowers Challenge is here to give you a creative outlet\, some st
 ructure\, and respite from your brain. \n\nWhen you pick up a brush\, pen
 \, or pencil \\(thread\, clay\, fabric…\\)\, your brain gets a rest and 
 becomes more alive and flexible. The world around you becomes more alive\
 ; you pick up on shades\, details\, and patterns all around you. Your in
 tuition gets stronger. And fear lessens\, anxiety fades\, and curiosity gr
 ows. You stop worrying about making mistakes\, and instead\, you find the
  freedom to simply create
URL:https://www.taradickinson.com/project-page/workshops
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Quantum Coherence with Anistara Ma Ka
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T183000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T203000
UID:2603062QbcQirXykybCmjCGZWEGg
DESCRIPTION:**Cultivating Wholeness Through Energy Alignment**\n\nDuring t
 hese gatherings\, Anistara will be sharing a meditation by Dr. Joe Dispenz
 a\, whose teachings she has practiced for years. Having attended two of hi
 s live retreats\, she witnessed profound transformations and healing stori
 es that deepened her devotion to coherence work and the intelligence of th
 e quantum field.\n\nEach session invites you into a state of heart–mind 
 coherence — where the nervous system settles\, the body relaxes\, and th
 e energy field begins to harmonize. Within the amplified energetic environ
 ment of the EES\, participants are guided to align with wholeness\, clarit
 y\, and expanded possibility.\n\nThis is not a lecture or workshop — it 
 is a space to practice. To breathe. To regulate.\n\nTo remember the innate
  intelligence within your body and energy system.\n\nWhether you are new t
 o meditation or experienced in quantum practices\, this monthly gathering 
 offers a consistent container to reset\, recalibrate\, and return to coher
 ence.\n\nCome as you are. Leave feeling aligned\, centered\, and more whol
 e.\n\n**About Anistara**\n\nAnistara Ma Ka is a multidimensional guide\, b
 est-selling author\, and transformational speaker devoted to supporting aw
 akening souls in remembering who they truly are. As the Founder of Ascensi
 on University and the Mother of 11.11 Unified\, she guides individuals int
 o embodied leadership\, sovereignty\, and alignment with New Earth conscio
 usness through her teachings\, transmissions\, and ceremonial work. An ord
 ained Sacred Portal Oracle of the Portal Priestess Mystery School and stew
 ard of Joy Oasis\, Anistara creates immersive retreats\, initiations\, and
  ceremonies rooted in ancient wisdom and modern embodiment. Her work weave
 s energetic leadership\, sacred remembrance\, and lived devotion—holding
  spaces where transformation unfolds naturally and participants reconnect 
 with their purpose\, presence\, and inner authority.
LOCATION:Energy Wave Center 
URL:https://energywavecenter.com/anistara/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
