DESCRIPTION:Inherited a rose garden in your new home? Gifted a rose withou
 t a label? Are you a collector or hobbyist needing accurate identification
  of a heritage/old rose? Whatever the mystery\, come join us for an inform
 ative and interactive program on how best to identify your rose. Free to a
 ttend!\n\nIf you have a mystery rose in your garden that's blooming\, plea
 se bring a cutting with you \\(don't forget the leaves!\\) or a high-quali
 ty picture from last season and our rosarians will teach you simple guidel
 ines on how to determine your rose variety and will offer care tips too!
