 r looking to add a new style to your repertoire\, this class will give you
  the tools to start enjoying Kizomba on the dance floor right away.\n\nDro
 p-in fee is $20 and no partner is required.\n\nDate & Time: Fridays @ 8:30
 PM – 9:30PM\n\nInstructor: Tyler Crandall\n\nAddress: 4140 Redwood Highw
 ay \\#8 San Rafael\, CA\n\nNote: Arrive 10 minutes before. No floor markin
 g shoe soles allowed.\n\nSocial dancing after class 9:30 pm – 11:30 pm
