BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Mary Blair: Mid-Century Magic Opening Celebration
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T160000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T190000
UID:260305E3VPud6Lu0aFzQmiEIsM9g
DESCRIPTION:The **Napa Valley Museum Yountville (NVMY)** invites you to
  step into a world of imagination and color as we celebrate the opening of
  **“*Mary Blair: Mid-Century Magic”*** on March 21\, 2026 —a specia
 l exhibition created by the Walt Disney Family Museum. Co-hosted by **NVM
 Y\, the Walt Disney Family Museum\, and Tiki Oasis**\, this opening celebr
 ation offers guests a first look into Mary Blair’s iconic playful palett
 es and whimsical spirit she brought to some of Disney’s most beloved mov
 ies.\n\nThroughout the evening\, delightful surprises will unfold\, includ
 ing a 60's inspired dance performance by **The** **Devil-Ettes\,** mid-c
 entury music by our resident DJ**\,** cocktails by **Hanson of Sonoma Dis
 tillery\,** and small bites by **Sushi Monkey.** Guests are encouraged
  to attend in **cocktail attire or mid-century 50s–60s style**. \n\n*
 *4 p.m. First Look for Priority Access\, Museum Member & MAC Pack** incl
 udes signature cocktail created by Hanson of Sonoma Distillery and gift fr
 om the NVMY\n\n**5-7 p.m. General Admission**: Celebration continues with
  cocktails\, sushi and music.\n\n*Join us as we toast to imagination and t
 he radiant legacy of Mary Blair.*
LOCATION:Napa Valley Museum Yountville
URL:https://napavalleymuseum.org/products/mary-blair-mid-century-modern-op
 ening-celebration
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
