DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T220000
UID:260218vdjqUGMTwEOK2-INVs6Yag
DESCRIPTION:Mercy Presents: Puff N’ Paint – Glow In The Dark Edition S
 aturday\, March 21\, 2026 | 7:00 PM – 10:00 PM 📍 The Lounge at Mercy\
 n\nTap into your creative flow at Mercy’s Glow-In-The-Dark Puff N’ Pai
 nt—a high-vibe\, black light–lit art experience where cannabis culture
 \, creativity\, and community collide inside The Lounge at Mercy.\n\nThis 
 isn’t your average paint night. Under immersive black lights\, neon and 
 glow-in-the-dark paints come alive as you sip\, puff\, and create in a rel
 axed\, visually electric atmosphere designed to spark imagination and conn
 ection. Whether you’re dialed into your canvas or vibing with the room\,
  this session is all about expression\, conversation\, and good energy—n
 o pressure\, just pure creative fun.\n\nGuided by smooth evening beats\, w
 atch your artwork transform as the lights go low and the glow turns on. Ex
 pect trippy colors\, luminous strokes\, and a one-of-a-kind masterpiece yo
 u’ll take home at the end of the night.\n\nPresented by Emerald Sky and 
 Papa’s Herb\, this immersive experience is your invitation to slow down\
 , light up\, and let your creativity glow—Mercy style.\n\n🎨 What’s 
 Included:\n\n- All glow-in-the-dark and neon painting supplies\n\n- Black 
 light–powered Puff N’ Paint experience\n\n- Zero-pressure creative ses
 sion\n\n- Take-home canvas masterpiece\n\n- Atmosphere buzzing with smooth
  evening beats\n\n- Cannabis-friendly lounge to spark creativity\n\n🎟 T
 icket Tiers:\n\nLimited to 80 guests\n\nGeneral Admission – $35 Includes
  paint supplies only\n\nVIP Tier 1 – $50 Includes $25 Goodie Bag\n\nVIP 
 Tier 2 – $75 Includes $50 Goodie Bag\n\n✨ Come for the glow. Stay for 
 the vibe. Leave with art that lights up the night.\n\n21\\+ Only | DCC \\#
  C12-0000420-LIC
LOCATION:The Lounge at Mercy
URL:https://www.themercylounge.com
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
