 ics with Soul'd Out Band! This talented band will take you on a musical jo
 urney through the decades with their eclectic mix of genres and styles. Fr
 om the soulful sounds of Stevie Wonder to the upbeat rhythm of Bruno Mars\
 , they've got something for everyone. Not only that\, but they also play a
 ll your favorite top 40 hits! Whether you're a fan of pop\, rock\, hip-hop
