UID:260307XZqhKeRRdUeQjQkavZZhAQ
DESCRIPTION:Dorothy Herger: Curiosities presents a selection of art and ar
 tifacts gathered over a lifetime of world travel. Spanning continents incl
 uding Africa\, Asia\, and South America\, the exhibition features baskets\
 , masks\, ceremonial objects\, and Dorothy Herger’s own ceramic works. T
 ogether\, these pieces form a deeply personal collection shaped by curiosi
 ty\, movement\, and care.\n\nAn opening reception will be held on March 8\
 , and Herger will give a at 2 p.m.
