BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tord Gustavsen Trio
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T193000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T220000
UID:260307PL9OPOTsHEafLNlqOT0NDw
DESCRIPTION:A rare opportunity to be up close and personal with the Tord G
 ustavsen Trio\n\n“A Norwegian pianist of lyrical and often halcyon sensi
 bilities” (NY Times)\, Gustavsen and his trio bring a stripped-down appr
 oach in which beauty and emotional intensity are united. His new ECM relea
 se\, Opening\, explores the concept of openness and taking inspiration fro
 m the forces that surround us.\n\nA pianist of poetic cast\, an exceptiona
 lly lucid player with a sure sense of melodic structure and an often-aston
 ishing lyrical imagination. - JazzTimes\n\nCool and mysterious\, pristine 
 and intensely emotional\, the music of Norwegian pianist Tord Gustavsen ha
 s earned a vast following while making few populist concessions. Easily th
 e most acclaimed composer and pianist on the Norwegian jazz scene\, he’s
  released a series of critically hailed albums that have climbed high on t
 he Norwegian pop charts\, starting with his 2003’s ECM debut Changing Pl
 aces.\n\n**URLs:**\n\nTickets: https://go.evvnt.com/3363109-0?pid=6298\n\n
 Website: https://go.evvnt.com/3363109-2?pid=6298\n\nFacebook: https://go.e
 vvnt.com/3363109-3?pid=6298\n\nInstagram: https://go.evvnt.com/3363109-4?p
 id=6298\n\n**Date and Time:** On Sun\, 22 Mar 2026 19:30 - Sun\, 22 Mar 20
 26 22:00\n\n**Venue Details:** Music And Minds\, 15 Kehoe Way\, Inverness\
 , California\, 94937\, United States\n\n**Category:** Live Music\n\n**Pric
 e:** Suggested Donation: USD 120.00\n\n**Artists:** TORD GUSTAVSEN\, STEIN
 AR RAKNES \, JARLE VEPESTAD
LOCATION:Music And Minds
URL:http://go.evvnt.com/3363109-2?pid=6298
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
