SUMMARY:Therapeutic Group Hypnosis
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T140000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T160000
UID:260304yhYO78gGxk-VSEmKmCKflQ
DESCRIPTION:Guided into the calm presence of the Self\, you’ll understan
 d protective patterns\, meet vulnerable inner parts with curiosity instead
  of shame\, and gently release old emotional burdens.\n\nThrough inner dia
 logue and symbolic repair\, exiled parts are welcomed back as strengths—
 supporting deeper self-acceptance\, integration\, and emotional freedom. 
  You will be lead through this experience in a light hypnotic trance that
  is very relaxing and allows for accessing deeper layers of the subconscio
 us mind.\n\nEostar will close the group hypnotherapy session with a sound 
 bath\, enveloping everyone is a sonic embrace of heart-bliss.\n\nReturn at
  5 PM and join Eostar to further deepen into your heart-bliss during her S
 ound Odyssey.\n\nSOUND ODYSSEY\n\nAbout EESystem™\n\nThe EESystem™ is 
 a ecologically & environmentally safe system used by individuals\, doctors
 \, and therapists as well as Meditation and Wellness Centers to improve hu
 man development and psychological well-being.  Decades of documented res
 earch on the EESystem™ shows people experience improved immune function\
 , relief from pain\, detoxification\, elevated moods\, increased energy\, 
 and much more.\n\nAbout Eostar\n\nEostar Kamala is a multifaceted healer a
 nd musician\, specializing in therapeutic hypnosis\, transformational shad
 ow work\, and sound healing. With certifications from the Hypnosis Motivat
 ion Institute as a Master Hypnotist and Hypnotherapist\, she blends her ex
 tensive education—including breathwork facilitation and shamanic trainin
 g—with her passion for guiding others through their inner journeys.\n\nH
 er spiritual awakening began at 19 in Hungary\, ignited by the wisdom of a
  local healer. This transformative experience led her to explore various h
 ealing modalities\, ultimately culminating in the founding of “Shadow In
 to Light” Hypnotherapy. Eostar’s artistry reflects her journey\; from 
 sacred music performances to visual art representing her inner landscapes\
 , she channels universal love through every medium.\n\nNow based in Mount 
 Shasta’s energy vortex\, Eostar continues to evolve as a teacher and fac
 ilitator of plant medicine ceremonies while sharing her devotional music w
 ith the world. Her mission is to empower others to embrace their own paths
  toward healing and self-discovery.\n\nDiscover more about the Eostar’s 
 service to humanity at: Eostar.net/hypnotherapy/
LOCATION:Energy Wave Center
URL:https://energywavecenter.com/eostar/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
