DESCRIPTION:Tired of the same conversations? Change the environment.\n\nTh
 is is speed dating\, rebuilt around movement.\n\n10 stations.\n\n6 minutes
  each.\n\nYou’ll rotate through every round—meeting each person while 
 you’re actually doing something.\n\nIt’s fast\, a little sweaty\, and 
 way more real than sitting across a table.\n\nNo pressure to perform. No n
 eed for perfect lines.\n\nJust show up\, move\, and talk.\n\nHow it works:
 \n\n10 stations\n\n6-minute rounds\n\n1-minute transitions\n\nYou’ll mee
 t all participants\n\nDetails:\n\nMarch 22nd — 10:30 AM\n\nLimited to 10
  men / 10 women\n\n$15 ticket\n\nAge-matched groups \\(within ~12 years\\)
 \n\nAfter the event\, you’ll be able to match with anyone you connected 
