BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:In Her Power
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T120000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T160000
UID:260225igcyU5csgEe_O7aJX_mVow
DESCRIPTION:In Her Power\n\nA Collaboration by Priscila Soares & JeanCheri
 e\n\nIn Her Power is a group exhibition celebrating women’s presence\, s
 trength\, and creative expression. Anchored by a collaborative\, life-size
  sculptural work by Priscila Soares and JeanCherie\, the exhibition brings
  together works by women artists exploring power as something lived\, embo
 died\, and deeply personal.\n\nAt the heart of the gallery stands a mounta
 in lioness woman — a guardian figure shaped by two artists working toget
 her\, each bringing her own voice\, materials\, and vision. Surrounding th
 is central work\, invited artists contribute pieces that reflect their own
  relationship to power\, resilience\, intuition\, and selfhood.\n\nRather 
 than offering a single definition\, In Her Power invites viewers to witnes
 s many expressions of strength — quiet and fierce\, ancestral and contem
 porary\, individual and shared. It is both a celebration of women artists 
 and an invitation to step into presence\, creativity\, and connection.\n\n
 Opening Reception:\n\nMarch 1\, 12–4pm\n\nGallery Hours:\n\nSundays in M
 arch\, 12–4pm\n\nLocation:\n\nMare Island Art Studios\n\n110 Pintado St.
 \n\nVallejo\, CA
LOCATION:Mare Island Art Studios
URL:https://mareislandartstudios.com/events/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
