 e needle felting as we now have all of the supplies. I now have supplies f
 or macrame too. Bring your favorite covered drink container for tea. Sit a
 nd Stitch is for people to come and work on any fiber arts activity that t
 hey have while visiting with others. Most people will bring their own proj
 ects\, but we always have hooks\, needles\, and yarn and sometimes we will
  offer a project with instructions that people may choose to make. Let us 
