UID:260305OloUslOvWUSudBmj0xh-oA
DESCRIPTION:**Tiny Hooves\, Big Hearts: Our Ongoing Rescue Mission**\n\n**
 At Goatlandia\, our mission is simple: to give love\, safety\, and a secon
 d chance to animals who need it most.**\n\n**We were recently called to re
 scue three baby goats. These tiny babies are now safe at Goatlandia\, and 
 they need bottle feeding several times a day to stay healthy and thrive.**
 \n\n**That’s Where You Come In: The Bottle Baby Breakfast Club**\n\n**St
 arting March 6th\, join us for a heartwarming hour on the farm\, bottle-fe
 eding and cuddling our newest rescues while supporting their care.**\n\n**
 Your $250 donation (covers milk and supplies for weeks of feedings) includ
 es admission for up to four guests for a private\, unforgettable visit to 
 Goatlandia.**\n\n**Come share the love\, feel the magic\, and help us give
  these little ones the future they deserve.**
LOCATION:Goatlandia
URL:https://www.goatlandia.org/bottle-babies-breakfast-club
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Beginning Improv Class
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260324T183000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260324T203000
UID:260304iaPrJ5F8WUqOvuli4BDdNw
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to 6-week introduction to the world of improv. It's su
 per fun\, playful and supportive!\n\nWe'll focus on games and exercises de
 signed to get us out of our judging minds and into a playful state of flow
 \, and start exploring scene work while learning the basic elements that m
 ake improv work. You'll learn to think on your feet \\(which actually mean
 s to STOP thinking\\)\, trust your instincts\, and work collaboratively wi
 th others. Expect lots of laughter\, spontaneity\, and unforgettable momen
 ts.\n\nYou don't consider yourself “naturally” quick\, funny or outgoi
 ng? Perfect! You don't need to be to do improv\, all you need to do is sho
 w up--truly! You will surprise yourself\, then watch your confidence grow.
  Improv tools can help us be more comfortable with ourselves\, thus enabli
 ng us to be more relaxed and engaged in our work\, social situations or on
 stage\, for those who perform or wish to.\n\nMostly it’s just really\, r
 eally fun!
LOCATION:Redwood Empire Ice Arena (Studio)
URL:https://www.ziplineimprov.com/current-classes
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
