 pact movements. We’ll also dedicate time to flexibility and balance\, be
 cause true fitness isn’t just about strength—it’s about moving throu
 gh the world with ease and confidence.\n\nMy promise to you is that you’
 ll leave here feeling stronger\, more energized\, and ready to take on you
 r week. There’s no pressure\, just progress\, and we move at a pace that
