UID:260224kdA35lX9lUurrNkWVTBImw
DESCRIPTION:🌴 SambaDá at HopMonk Tavern Novato\n\nFriday\, March 27 | 
 Doors 7pm · Show 8pm | 21\\+ | $25\n\nSanta Cruz’s beloved Brazilian gr
 oove collective SambaDá returns to HopMonk Novato with a high-energy nigh
 t of Afro-Brazilian rhythms\, deep grooves\, and nonstop dancing.\n\nBlend
 ing samba\, funk\, reggae\, and global beats\, SambaDá brings the kind of
  show that turns a concert into a full-on dance party. Expect sweat\, smil
 es\, and serious movement on the dance floor.\n\nCome early\, grab a drink
 \, bring your crew—and get ready to move. This one’s for the dancers. 
 💃🔥
LOCATION:HopMonk Tavern Novato
