 n downtown Healdsburg\, featuring live music\, award-winning wine\, and bo
 ld street-style food. Our Music\, Wine & Dine Night pairs the fun\, crowd-
 pleasing sounds of Rock on a Roll with the flavorful dishes of Lila’s St
 reetside Eats.\n\nRock on a Roll brings an upbeat mix of familiar favorite
 s and danceable tunes\, creating the perfect soundtrack for a relaxed and 
 social evening surrounded by barrels and warm winery ambiance. Enjoy Longb
 oard’s wines by the glass or bottle while Lila’s Streetside Eats serve
 s fresh\, creative street food made to order and packed with flavor.\n\nFr
 iday | 5:00 PM – 7:00 PM Free entry\n\nPlease note: This is an over-21 e
 vent inside the Barrel Room. Under-21 guests and leashed pets are welcome 
 on the patio only.\n\nCome grab a seat early and enjoy a classic Sonoma Co
 unty night of great music\, great wine\, and great food.\n\nWine available
  for purchase Live music by Rock on a Roll Food by Lila’s Streetside Eat
 s (street-style comfort food) Location: Longboard Vineyards Barrel Room Ad
 dress: 5 Fitch Street\, Healdsburg\, CA 95448
