 olores Huerta.\n\nWe’ll have volunteer activities from 9 a.m. to noon.\n
 \nSign up for a spot at Calendly.com/PetalumaBounty\n\nKids are welcome w
 ith an accompanying adult.\n\nAs César Chávez Day\, March 31\, approache
 s\, we reflect on the legacy of Chávez and Huerta\, who bravely fought t
