BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:An Evening in Seville! Rotary Fundraiser
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T170000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T220000
UID:260121F90I_fTCe0yXvZzmHT4gCQ
DESCRIPTION:Windsor Rotary Community Foundation Fundraiser\n\nEmpowering W
 indsor Youth\n\nSaturday\, March 28 • 5–10 PM • Huerta Gym\, Downtow
 n Windsor\n\nJoin the Windsor Rotary Community Foundation for an unforgett
 able evening dedicated to strengthening our community and uplifting the ne
 xt generation. On Saturday\, March 28\, Huerta Gym transforms into a vibra
 nt celebration filled with rich flavors\, dynamic entertainment\, and a sh
 ared commitment to Empowering Windsor Youth.\n\nGuests will enjoy a delici
 ous spread of tapas\, paella\, wine\, and beer\, creating the perfect sett
 ing for connection and celebration. Special guest Flamenco dancers will ig
 nite the room with the artistry and passion of Spain\, setting the tone fo
 r an evening steeped in culture and community spirit.\n\nAt the heart of t
 he night is our Silent & Live Auction\, featuring unique items\, experienc
 es\, and local treasures—all raising essential funds for youth programs 
 that shape Windsor’s future.\n\nHELP FUND THESE PROGRAMS & MORE\n\nWinds
 or Unified School District\n\n- Windsor Middle School AVID Program\n\n- AA
 C Communication Devices – Special Education\n\n- Windsor Middle School F
 arm to Table Program\n\n- Windsor Middle School Student Theatre Program\n\
 n- 5th Grade Science Camp at Nature Bridge Golden Gate\n\nCommunity & Yout
 h Development Partners\n\n- Circuit Riders – Ecological Restoration & Wo
 rkforce Training Center\n\n- Chief Doug Williams Gazebo – Mark West Area
  Community Park\n\n- Pacific Coast Air Museum – Student STEM Enrichment 
 Program\n\n…and many more programs that inspire\, empower\, and open doo
 rs for Windsor’s youth.\n\nEVENT EXPERIENCE\n\nImmerse yourself in the v
 ibrant flavors and traditions of Seville with live music\, passionate flam
 enco performances\, and both silent & live auctions that bring the communi
 ty together for a powerful cause.\n\nWhat’s Included\n\n- Flamenco Perfo
 rmances\n\n- Wine & Beer\n\n- Tapas & Paella\n\n- Live Music\n\n- Silent A
 uction\n\n- Live Auction\n\nEvening Highlights\n\n- Authentic Spanish cuis
 ine featuring delectable tapas and paella\n\n- Exhilarating flamenco perfo
 rmances\n\n- Silent & live auctions with one‑of‑a‑kind items\n\n- Sp
 ecial guests and unforgettable entertainment\n\n- Stunning casetas‑style
  décor inspired by Seville’s iconic Feria de Abril\n\nWe are actively a
 ccepting sponsorship support and donations of food\, beer\, wine\, and auc
 tion items.\n\nMore Details: http://www.windsorrotary.org/an-evening-in-se
 ville.../\n\nWHY YOUR SUPPORT MATTERS\n\nWith youth services facing increa
 sing challenges and budget cuts\, Rotary remains steadfast in its mission 
 to protect and expand opportunities for young people in our community. You
 r support—whether through sponsorship\, auction donations\, or attending
  the event—directly fuels these programs and keeps them thriving.\n\nTog
 ether\, we can make a meaningful impact. Together\, we can raise up our yo
 uth. Together\, we can build a stronger\, brighter future for Windsor.\n\n
 Join the fun. Join the movement. Join us in empowering Windsor’s youth.\
 n\nABOUT ROTARY\n\nWindsor Rotary provides year‑round support to our com
 munity. We rely on the generosity and involvement of neighbors like you to
  continue this important work. Discover more about our club and the people
  who help make Windsor one of the best places to call home.
LOCATION:Huerta Gymnasium
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/an-evening-in-seville-r
 otary-fundraiser/17920100/2026-03-28T17
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
