DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T170000
UID:260114Ym8uP14BA06hgqQMTFhypw
DESCRIPTION:GT racing returns to Wine Country! Join us at Sonoma Raceway f
 or a full weekend featuring:\n\n GT World Challenge America powered by AW
 S  GT America powered by AWS  Pirelli GT4 America  TC America powered b
 y Skip Barber  Toyota GR Cup North America  McLaren Trophy America\n\nEn
 joy nonstop racing\, open paddock access\, fan activities\, food\, drinks\
