DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260329T000000
UID:260224N3Ef--A23UK7XjKgxeLPsQ
DESCRIPTION:After the breakup of The Beatles\, John performed live on a ha
 ndful of occasions but\, unlike the other three Beatles\,\n\nwould never h
 ave the chance to seriously tour. In interviews given in 1980\, with the r
 elease of the Double\n\nFantasy album\, John spoke of going on tour again.
   \n\nImagine John Lennon unplugged…\n\nThere is much about John Lennon 
 that people may not know - his songs and the stories behind them.\n\nAccom
 panied on piano by Tommy Cosentino
