BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Nattali Rize
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260329T180000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260329T000000
UID:260224MNrfDsekckWG-MsBW6Y4Dw
DESCRIPTION:“… Enuff corporate noise in the ears of the youth … Time
  to spread the Truth.” \n\nWith a deep Reggae Influence the Nattali Rize
  band bring heavy beats & conscious rebel lyrics to a progressive electron
 ic\, roots\, reggae\, dub foundation. But this is more than genre labels\;
  The music\, message & intention trancends all that\, forget the borders a
 nd waters that divide us\, the movement is to ignite the great remembrance
  of who we are\, our collective power\, what we can be\, to break the ment
 al conditioning and find full freedom in this lifetime.\n\nThe Nattali Riz
 e project launched out of Jamaica into the US\, EU and beyond in 2014 with
  a strong run of captivating festival performances and national club shows
 . Now with tours alongside the likes of Michael Franti and Spearhead\, Kat
 chafire\, Third World\, J-Boog\, Julian Marley\, Tribal Seeds and more und
 er their belt\, the worldwide movement is ever rizing!\n\nThis is a global
  mash up of raw energy and vibe that together has been rocking stages sinc
 e the band first burst onto the scene in 2015.\n\nAsk Nattali where she co
 mes from\, she’ll tell you “All Directions”\, with no fixed address\
 , Nattali is now based where the music takes her\, Nattali Rize claims not
  to belong to any nation state\, but to the ever-evolving community of awa
 kening consciousness. The global mission - to uplift\, unify consciousness
  & Rize together\n\n“Nattali is a bright light in the world with a visio
 n that extends beyond the stage.”- Michael Franti \\(Spearhead\\)\n\nNat
 tali Rize is recognised globally for her unwavering commitment to using he
 r voice and music for the global shift toward Full Freedom and the movemen
 t of Truth and Justice over the systemic exploitation of the people and ou
 r planet. \n\n."Our intention with our music is to ignite that memory in o
 urselves of our individual and collective power to live life to the fulles
 t and recognize our selves and each other as evolving beings of light. A r
 eality of Full Freedom is a possibility on this earth and in these times. 
 We use music to sound frequencies infused with this idea\, and to resonate
  at a higher level than what is currently being permeated across current w
 orld culture. People are powerful\; we want them to reclaim that power and
  no longer be servants to a system that has never\, and will never\, serve
  them to their fullest potential. As such\, our frequency in this system i
 s a rebel …  Rebel Music\, Rebel Frequencies we deal with!” - Nattali 
 Rize.\n\nThe debut album Rebel Frequency\, released in May 2018 is availab
 le on all platforms now.\n\nDecember 2018 also sees the release of the off
 icial merchandise through the bands brand Rize Nation Wear.\n\n“One of t
 he nation’s most refreshing voices” - Rolling Stone.\n\n“INFECTIOUS!
 ”- NPR
LOCATION:HopMonk Tavern
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/1037057720?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=2
 87&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
